text: Russell Begaye is a Navajo politician. He was the 8th president of Navajo Nation from May 2015 to January 2019. He was elected to the office on April 4, 2015 and was sworn in on May 12, 2015. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Politicians from New Mexico Category:Politicians from Arizona Category:Presidents of the Navajo Nation Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
